- The offer's fair.

02:24.349 --> 02:27.519
Off the record, the O.S.I.
will help you with your sting.

02:27.519 --> 02:29.269
The rest is up to your decoy.

02:29.269 --> 02:32.609
- You guarantee the Venture's safety?
- 100% guaranteed.

02:32.609 --> 02:35.999
