a lot of things ... many things.

04:21.019 --> 04:23.789
You don't have a child, Mr. Monarch.
So I figured.

04:23.789 --> 04:25.349
You ... You know who I am?

04:25.359 --> 04:27.889
What ... you've heard
of the Mighty Monarch?

04:27.889 --> 04:29.459
Oh, of course.
Big fan of your work.

04:29.459 --> 04:31.829
That marionette thing
you made for Rusty Venture?

04:31.829 --> 04:35.059
- Wonderful.
- Wow, I-I'm flattered.

04:35.069 --> 04:37.129
I... Red Death knows my work.

04:37.139 --> 04:40.169
- I mean, that's like ...
- That's my business.

04:40.169 --> 04:42.709
But we're not at the office
right now, you see.

04:42.709 --> 04:46.079
And that's the secret. You got to
separate your work from your life.

04:46.079 --> 04:49.299
It's a slippery slope once you
start living as your character.

04:49.299 --> 04:52.419
The obsession starts, the darkness ...

04:52.579 --> 04:55.969
a man can do terrible things
when he's lost his way.

04:55.969 --> 04:58.299
Terrible things.

05:02.559 --> 05:04.589
