a self-destruct button?

05:15.569 --> 05:18.739
- This is madness!
- How's it hanging, tough guy?

05:18.739 --> 05:20.689
Gah! What is going on here?

05:20.699 --> 05:23.699
Reel it in, Hatred.
This is a covert military action.

05:23.699 --> 05:26.279
Lock this place up,
take the rest of the day off,

05:26.279 --> 05:30.199
and, uh, watch where you
point that flashlight.

05:34.179 --> 05:37.629
What the hell?!
I said we were having supper at 4:00!

05:37.629 --> 05:41.259
- And it's 4:30!
- What is it, Thanksgiving or something?!

05:41.269 --> 05:42.629
Who eats dinner at 4:00?!

05:42.629 --> 05:45.099
Supper! Not dinner!
Supper! I said supper!

05:45.099 --> 05:46.999
- Oh, sorry, honey.
- Supper!

05:47.009 --> 05:49.839
I was late because
I was talking to... Red Death.

05:49.839 --> 05:51.859
God, what the...?
How did that happen?!

05:51.899 --> 05:55.709
Right? And he is the
sweetest man in the world

05:55.709 --> 05:58.509
and terrifying.
You wouldn't believe it.

05:58.519 --> 06:00.919
- He is so awesome.
- What are we gonna do?

06:00.919 --> 06:02.319
I'm not gonna kill him.
No way.

06:02.319 --> 06:04.749
No, we can't kill him.
I'll tell you that right now.

06:04.759 --> 06:06.059
The man is a treasure.

06:06.059 --> 06:09.929
If we do anything sinister,
he will murder us in our sleep.

06:09.929 --> 06:12.629
But your mighty leader
has come up with a plan.

06:12.629 --> 06:14.499
Hang on,
I've been in traffic all day.

06:14.499 --> 06:16.329
I got to piss like Secretariat here.

06:16.329 --> 06:18.499
No, Manolo hasn't finished
the downstairs bathroom yet.

06:18.499 --> 06:22.249
- You got to use the upstairs one.
- Fine.

06:22.259 --> 06:23.559
Here ...
turn around. Don't look.

06:23.559 --> 06:25.139
What?! No!

06:25.139 --> 06:27.179
- Don't piss in the sink.
- I think you mean,

06:27.179 --> 06:28.979
