06:32.349 --> 06:34.179
<i>Small world, isn't it?</i>

06:34.189 --> 06:38.019
Me, a handsome billionaire
playboy super scientist,

06:38.019 --> 06:41.489
you, sent here to help me.
Maybe not sent.

06:41.489 --> 06:43.939
Maybe you're here
because you want to be.

06:43.949 --> 06:47.279
Because you're drawn here... to me.

06:47.279 --> 06:49.919
Um, we need the civilians out of here.

06:54.259 --> 06:56.369
All right, let's get
this dog and pony show

06:56.369 --> 06:59.039
on the damn road already.
Snoopy, give me chatter!

06:59.039 --> 07:02.879
The bait, a.k.a. Red Death,
is in Long Island preparing.

07:02.879 --> 07:05.379
- No movement.
- What? You're tracking agents of the Guild?

07:05.379 --> 07:08.799
How dare you!
Like dogs sniffing a cannon barrel,

07:08.799 --> 07:11.939
- you will regret your ...
- Whoa, whoa, nobody's tracking anybody!

07:11.939 --> 07:13.389
