the Blue Morpho.

07:22.069 --> 07:26.699
- How are the decoys going?
- Wow, it's like looking into a mirror.

07:26.699 --> 07:30.489
Yeah, if the members of
Grand Funk Railroad were behind us.

07:30.489 --> 07:34.209
Yeah, uh, these disguise kits
haven't been used since the '70s.

07:34.209 --> 07:37.049
There's a whole bag
of false sideburns in there.

07:37.049 --> 07:39.949
- What happened to your eye?
- We had them removed and replaced

07:39.949 --> 07:43.719
- with a conduit to our display goggle.
- They never stop itching.

07:43.719 --> 07:45.169
I'm gonna set you up right.

07:45.169 --> 07:48.839
Now, I could dump you into a
blue speed suit and call it a day,

07:48.839 --> 07:51.389
or we could do this right,
do this with panache.

07:51.399 --> 07:53.099
Dean, go get your sweater vest.

07:53.099 --> 07:56.849
- Classic model Hank and Dean!
- I'm on it!

07:56.849 --> 07:59.769
- Uh, your red eye is blinking.
- It is? Oh, great!

07:59.769 --> 08:02.939
That's an e-mail I can't
read till I put on my goggle.

08:02.939 --> 08:04.939
- One, two, three, shoot!
- Once, twice, three, shoot!

08:04.939 --> 08:07.989
- Rock. You lose. One, two, three, shoot!
- Once, twice, three, shoot!

