might be able to sneak you out some.

08:39.779 --> 08:42.029
I got your back. Wink.

08:42.029 --> 08:44.058
You gotta stop that, Billy.

08:46.119 --> 08:48.979
Don't eat that.
He's testing you.

08:48.989 --> 08:50.399
What, are you kidding?!
I'm starving!

08:50.399 --> 08:52.459
There's little hats on the
chicken legs and everything.

08:52.459 --> 08:54.119
