- He did. He's a baby killer.

12:13.399 --> 12:14.899
Killed a sweet little baby.

12:14.899 --> 12:17.599
It was a werewolf!
A werewolf!

12:17.599 --> 12:21.349
- It looked like a rabid animal.
- Yeah, that's what he says.

12:21.349 --> 12:23.239
But what I saw
was a wee little baby,

12:23.239 --> 12:26.319
just laying there with
a silver bullet in his brain.

12:26.329 --> 12:28.579
- Wee little baby.
- Werewolf!

12:28.579 --> 12:30.439
I saved your damn life!

12:30.449 --> 12:32.329
Oh, thank you, Rodney.

12:32.329 --> 12:36.779
