13:00.279 --> 13:03.309
Okay, hunter.
Time to rock and roll.

13:03.309 --> 13:05.309
That felt cool when I said that.

13:06.699 --> 13:10.169
Doctor Venture!
Face your doom!

13:12.459 --> 13:15.069
Oh, my goodness!
Red Death!

13:15.069 --> 13:18.909
I'm frightened
because I'm Dr. Venture!

13:18.909 --> 13:20.409
Help me, Brock!

13:20.409 --> 13:22.329
Beep, beep-boo-boo-boo-beep,
beep, beep!

13:22.329 --> 13:24.579
<i>Go Team Venture!</i>

13:31.139 --> 13:35.429
- He's using live rounds!
- Cool! We should do this more!

13:47.519 --> 13:50.689
- Now that looks really fun.
- I love swimming at night.

13:50.929 --> 13:53.679
No, really.
I think I've met you before.

13:53.689 --> 13:55.019
Wh-What's your job?

13:55.019 --> 13:56.849
What is yours?
Professional nosey guy?

13:56.859 --> 13:58.609
You need to mind
your own beeswax.

13:58.609 --> 14:01.019
Do you mind beeswax for a living?
Get out of my wax.

14:01.029 --> 14:04.189
N-No.
I-I swear I've met you before.

14:04.199 --> 14:06.029
It's totally impossible.
I'm a loner.

14:06.029 --> 14:09.169
Yeah, okay, sorry.
I'm just under a lot of stress.

14:09.169 --> 14:11.619
Hey, could you warm this up?
It got cold.

14:11.619 --> 14:13.339
Sure.

14:14.869 --> 14:17.209
I knew it!
Maestro Wave!

14:17.209 --> 14:18.879
I fucking knew it!
You're a super villain!

14:18.879 --> 14:21.679
Okay, I'm a super villain.
Big whoop.

14:21.679 --> 14:23.549
So am I!
I'm the Termite!

14:23.549 --> 14:24.879
You know, with the ...
the helmet?

14:24.879 --> 14:27.429
- I-I'm the ... I'm the Termite!
- The Termite?

14:27.439 --> 14:30.299
Wait, with those gross mouth
grabby things on the helmet?

14:30.309 --> 14:33.559
Yes! Maxilla palps!
Those are my maxilla palps!

14:33.559 --> 14:35.309
Dude!
Eat our way out of here!

14:35.309 --> 14:37.279
You can tunnel out!
Eat me out!

14:37.279 --> 14:39.529
No, wait. No. I ...
you know what I mean.

14:39.529 --> 14:40.729
Just ... tunnel!

14:40.729 --> 14:42.649
I need the helmet.
That's how I ...

14:42.649 --> 14:44.229
I'm not really a Termite, dude.

14:44.239 --> 14:47.569
I, uh, approximate a
Termite's powers with a helmet.

14:47.569 --> 14:50.409
<i>I felt like I could've been
more in the moment,</i>

14:50.409 --> 14:54.159
- more present, you know?
- Let the neckerchief be your inspiration.

14:54.159 --> 14:56.799
Oh, don't be so hard on yourselves.

14:56.799 --> 14:58.279
Do you know if we're gonna do a reset?

14:58.279 --> 15:01.719
- Oh, gee. I tripped. Oops.
- Whoa, ow!

15:01.719 --> 15:03.799
Oh, sorry. That's mine.

15:03.809 --> 15:05.589
Hello. Red Death.

15:05.589 --> 15:07.929
<i>Your child and your
wife have been kidnapped.</i>

15:07.929 --> 15:10.229
<i>Sign away your arching
rights to Dr. Venture</i>

15:10.229 --> 15:12.599
<i>and they will be returned
safely in the morning.</i>

15:12.599 --> 15:14.649
<i>- If you don't ...
- I don't know who you are,</i>

15:14.649 --> 15:16.769
<i>but you have made
a very large mistake.</i>

15:16.769 --> 15:19.319
I have a very particular
set of skills ...

15:19.319 --> 15:22.269
skills I have acquired
over a very long career,

15:22.269 --> 15:25.239
skills that make me a nightmare
for people like you.

15:25.239 --> 15:28.249
Release my family, and that
will be the end of this.

15:28.249 --> 15:30.659
But if you don't, I will look for you,

15:30.669 --> 15:34.329
I will find you, and I will kill you.

15:34.339 --> 15:40.089
<i>Uh, okay, um... sorry?</i>

15:40.139 --> 15:41.189
- Ah, that was so scary!
- Ah!

15:41.189 --> 15:43.139
- That was so scary!
- Oh, God! Oh, my God!

15:43.149 --> 15:45.649
- That was so scary! Scary!
- That was so fucking terrifying.

15:45.649 --> 15:48.529
- We have to let them go!
- We don't have them! We can't let them go!

15:48.529 --> 15:51.819
He's gonna go all Liam Neeson!
He's gonna vaporize us!

15:51.919 --> 15:55.989
Your father always collected
friends ... presidents, movie stars.

15:55.989 --> 15:59.989
The man slept with Grace Kelly!
He even owned a boxer.

15:59.999 --> 16:01.999
So, the Blue Morpho was one of those.

16:01.999 --> 16:03.959
Well, there's no way
this new Blue Morpho

16:03.969 --> 16:06.999
is the old Blue Morpho.
It's probably somebody like him ...

16:06.999 --> 16:11.089
someone with something to prove,
maybe even someone we know.

16:11.089 --> 16:14.259
- Right, Rust?
- Well, original Blue Morpho is dead.

16:14.259 --> 16:17.179
I remember Jonas
was beside himself with grief.

16:17.179 --> 16:20.899
Kano, too, obviously.
He even cried.

16:20.899 --> 16:23.519
Kano? My dad's big, mute,
Asian bodyguard Kano?

16:23.519 --> 16:25.189
That guy had no emotions at all.

16:25.189 --> 16:27.189
- Why did he care?
- Oh, my God, Rusty!

16:27.189 --> 16:29.909
How do you not know that
they are the same Kano?

16:29.909 --> 16:31.439
It's in the Jonas Venture comics.

16:31.439 --> 16:33.909
Kano joined Team Venture
when Blue Morpho was possessed

16:33.909 --> 16:35.749
by an alien virus that made him evil.

16:35.749 --> 16:39.119
I wouldn't believe everything
you read in those comics, Billy.

16:39.119 --> 16:42.789
Except where it says I kicked
ass, 'cause I kicked ass!

16:42.789 --> 16:47.539
Well, I'm gonna join the old people
and your boyfriend and get to bed.

16:47.539 --> 16:50.459
Don't be such a stranger, Rust.
You're family.

16:51.099 --> 16:53.379
Well, heading home as well.

16:53.379 --> 16:55.849
I'm sure the Blue Morpho sting
was a wash out.

16:55.849 --> 16:57.219
Of course it was.

16:57.219 --> 17:00.519
Because the Blue Morpho
never showed up, did he? Wink!

17:00.519 --> 17:05.608
Whatever. Say good night to
your "boyfriend" for me. Wink!

17:05.898 --> 17:07.898
- We can work this out!
- There is no other way.

17:07.898 --> 17:09.898
- There's so many other ways!
- This is what he wants.

17:09.898 --> 17:11.449
- It's his plan for me.
- We could set a trap!

17:11.449 --> 17:13.529
- I'm so sorry.
- You don't have to do what he says!

17:13.539 --> 17:15.868
- You have to die. It's his plan.
- You have free will!

17:15.868 --> 17:17.618
He needs me to feed on your butt.

17:17.618 --> 17:19.118
- Oh, please don't!
- I'm sorry.

17:19.118 --> 17:20.608
<i>Oh, God! No!</i>

17:26.299 --> 17:30.249
I know you're there, Blue Morpho!

17:30.919 --> 17:33.669
Return my family or die!

17:35.339 --> 17:37.259
No, no, no!
We can explain!

17:37.259 --> 17:39.929
- Don't vaporize us!
- Your family is at your mother in-law's!

17:39.929 --> 17:42.809
I swear! Call there!
I swear we didn't touch them!

17:42.819 --> 17:47.319
You'd better be telling me the truth,
because I swear to ...

17:47.319 --> 17:49.519
Carol?
Hi, hi. Is Kate there?

17:49.519 --> 17:51.099
Yes, I'm fine.

17:51.109 --> 17:53.239
Uh, th-there's a bag
in the trunk of the car,

17:53.239 --> 17:56.459
but can you get Kate, please?
Lila needs her corn chips.

17:57.579 --> 17:59.279
Kate, Kate, are you ...

17:59.279 --> 18:01.449
Well, I-I told her
that there's some in ...

18:01.449 --> 18:03.529
Sweetie, they don't go stale
overnight.

18:03.539 --> 18:05.839
Okay, look, I'll ...
I'll come pick you up soon.

18:05.839 --> 18:08.839
Yes, yes, I'll get more on the way.
Love you, too.

18:08.839 --> 18:11.259
See? Everything is fine.

18:13.049 --> 18:16.009
So, why doesn't the Monarch
tell me everything...

18:16.019 --> 18:18.129
from the beginning.

18:21.189 --> 18:23.299
Well, look who's still here!

18:23.309 --> 18:26.139
Waiting for the good doctor, I assume?

18:26.139 --> 18:27.889
Nope. I don't have time
for your garbage tonight.

18:27.889 --> 18:29.309
I just got stood up,

18:29.309 --> 18:32.809
and I am so tired of him
making a fool out of me.

18:32.819 --> 18:35.229
I am going to go look
for the Blue Morpho.

18:35.229 --> 18:41.199
I will find him,
and I will kill him myself.

18:42.879 --> 18:45.659
And that was supposed to be
really dramatic,

18:45.659 --> 18:47.999
and I just blew it.
What button do I push here?

18:47.999 --> 18:50.799
Is it the star, the "L," the one?

18:51.719 --> 18:52.969
Service!

18:52.969 --> 18:54.469
<i>And a return volley!</i>

18:54.469 --> 18:55.969
<i>Me, me! Throw it to me!
Spike it!</i>

18:55.969 --> 18:57.469
<i>- Yes!
- Nice!</i>

18:57.469 --> 19:00.139
- Guess who's peeing?
- Well, what is this?!

19:00.139 --> 19:02.729
Good guys against the bad guys!
We're winning!

19:02.729 --> 19:06.099
- Why are you on the bad guy's side?
- 'Cause Phantom Limb left in a huff.

19:06.099 --> 19:07.849
But mostly 'cause we're winning.

19:08.429 --> 19:11.269
Fuck it.
Who wants a doc-tail?

19:11.269 --> 19:15.819
<i>The master mixologist in the house!
Hold on tight!</i>

19:15.819 --> 19:18.029
<i>Yeah, that's what I should've done.</i>

19:18.029 --> 19:21.749
But, I stayed.
Call it loyalty. Call it dumb.

19:21.749 --> 19:23.949
And she walked all over me.

19:23.949 --> 19:26.279
Women.
You don't deserve that.

19:26.289 --> 19:28.419
Nobody understands me like you.

19:28.419 --> 19:31.869
<i>It's who I am,
without this hate, I'm nothing.</i>

19:31.869 --> 19:34.929
I'm not like you.
I can't just turn this off.

19:34.929 --> 19:37.709
I'm the man who hates
Dr. Venture, period.

19:37.709 --> 19:39.709
We're all villains, Monarch,

19:39.719 --> 19:43.379
and with rules, we get to
spill blood and taste victory.

19:43.389 --> 19:47.799
Heck, I really wanted to kill
someone tonight, you know?

19:47.809 --> 19:50.359
But... rules.
They help us hate.

19:50.359 --> 19:52.109
Yeah, I tried to tell him that.

19:52.109 --> 19:54.729
Oh, shut up.
This was your idea.

19:54.729 --> 19:57.199
I was young once too, Monarch.

19:57.199 --> 20:02.619
I hated Professor Cadmium so bad.
It was all I thought about.

20:02.619 --> 20:05.409
But, you know, I found a way
to deal with my obsession.

20:05.409 --> 20:07.739
What did you do?
I'll try anything at this point.

20:07.739 --> 20:11.709
I took a deep breath,
I marched right up to him,

20:11.709 --> 20:13.329
looked him right in the eye

20:13.329 --> 20:15.579
then crushed
his skull with my bare hands!

20:15.579 --> 20:17.379
Before I burned his house
to the ground,

20:17.389 --> 20:20.389
I slaughtered his entire family.

20:20.389 --> 20:23.219
And you're the first to know that.

20:23.229 --> 20:26.639
Finish your task, Blue Morpho,
then change your ways.

20:26.649 --> 20:28.649
You are so ...

20:28.649 --> 20:31.399
If I were a woman,
I would never stop calling you.

20:31.399 --> 20:33.179
Dude, I don't get how
you can kill like that, though.

20:33.189 --> 20:35.769
Like, don't you ever feel sad?

20:35.769 --> 20:38.819
Me? You've killed a list of
villains from what I've heard.

20:38.819 --> 20:43.939
Well, not quite. Um...
I got to show you guys something.

20:50.949 --> 20:54.869
For you, my masters!

20:54.869 --> 20:57.419
I am all villains now!

20:57.429 --> 20:59.509
- What is your bidding?
- What happened in here?!

20:59.509 --> 21:02.799
- You guys weren't supposed to kill each other!
- Oh, that's a real ...

21:02.799 --> 21:05.629
You know, if you don't mind,

21:05.629 --> 21:10.889
I could solve your problem
and feed my... problem, as well.

21:10.889 --> 21:14.309
<i>- I'll only need a few minutes.
- Yeah, sure. Just clean up the bodies</i>

21:14.309 --> 21:16.889
<i>with your vaporizing trick
when you're done or something.</i>

21:18.149 --> 21:20.059
Ow! I didn't know!

21:20.069 --> 21:22.149
Why didn't you tell me we
had a bathroom down here?

21:50.179 --> 21:53.899
<i>When we meet again,
it will be as enemies, won't it? </i>

21:53.899 --> 21:56.319
No. Never!
You're my friend.

21:56.319 --> 21:58.899
You're my ... my best friend.

21:58.899 --> 22:01.149
Don't, man.
It's ... it's too hard.

22:01.159 --> 22:04.659
How will I know you if we
meet again? I must know.

22:05.779 --> 22:08.529
Because you'll see this ...
the woman who loves you.

22:08.529 --> 22:12.529
Yes, I am a woman.
And how will I recognize you?

22:14.119 --> 22:16.869
Because I had the top
of my skull removed,

22:16.869 --> 22:20.399
and I have this plastic dome
with tubes coming out of it.

